Game.....: Army Men Sarge's Heroes
Origin...: USA - NTSC
Released.: November 1st, 2000
Ripped.......: Nothing

Utilizing an amazing variety of mouth-watering animations, plastic toy soldiers have come to life on the Dreamcast. Sarge, the hero of the Green Army, attacks across countertops, through hallways, and into the backyard, fighting for the Green way of life. For if the Tan manages to secure the explosive sky rockets, horrific magnifying glasses, or the dreaded Garbage Disposal, the balance between good and evil could be shifted forever. It's Real Combat. 
Plastic Men. 